parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the air bag warning light can indicate a malfunction in the air bag system, which can lead to the failure of the air bags to deploy in the event of a crash, potentially causing injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The air bag warning light illuminates
the service air bag warning message is displayed
the air bag sensor needs to be cleaned or replaced
the air bag impact sensor fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking of the dashboard can lead to a safety hazard, as it can cause the air bag to deploy improperly or not deploy at all, potentially causing injuries or fatalities.

cracks on the passenger side air bag

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air bags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The air bags did not deploy in a crash
the seat belt did not lock
the air bag system indicated a malfunction
the air bag system needed to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the glow plugs can cause poor engine performance, decreased fuel efficiency, and increased emissions.

often near the airbag compartment or defrost air duct.
